## Workspace conventions

- **Date stamps:** ISO format (YYYY-MM-DD), <<EDIT: your local timezone, e.g. America/Toronto>> unless noted. Always use a real-time tool — never hardcode dates.
- **Filename versioning:** when a major artifact gets restructured, save the prior version as `<name>-vN-YYYY-MM-DD.<ext>` in `Strategy/z-archived/`.
- **Don't create new docs reflexively.** Trigger existing artifacts (Evidence Ledger, Strat Summary, Pyramid) first; only create a new file if there is genuinely no existing place for it.
- **Source-cite every claim** in any strategy doc — file path, transcript timestamp, email date. Claims without sources are guesses.

